{"tid":2332594,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[回帶]GC大獎 公布得獎名單 Cyberpunk 2077獲 5 獎","createTime":"2020-12-19T17:40:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T06:00:16.000Z","uid":13100,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5e7866811361ae6754961c95361a4760e002fe9b","tid":2332594,"uid":13100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T17:40:55.000Z","msg":"今年因為 COVID-19 疫情影響而改採數位活動形式舉辦的歐洲最大電玩展「gamescom」，於 8 月 30 日閉幕當天揭曉了今年 gamescom award 2020 的得獎名單，其中《電馭叛客 2077》獲得 GC 最佳大獎、最佳 PC 遊戲獎、最佳 RPG 獎、消費者最期待獎、最佳 PlayStation 獎等 5 個獎項的肯定，成為最大的贏家。<br />\n<br />\n  gamescom award 是針對 gamescom 參展遊戲進行評選的獎項。今年的 gamescom award 由德國和國際遊戲記者、知名 YouTuber 和其他專家組成的評審團從 140 多件參賽作品中，針對 26 個類別進行評選。除了評選獎項之外，並開放玩家票選獎項的投票。最後於 8 月 30 日的 &ldquo;最佳展出&rdquo; 直播節目中揭曉得獎名單。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=202505\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2Fdetail.php%3Fsn%3D202505&d=XkDMRo5st5VLQkVJYuplWJNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=4e9f685b\" target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=202505</a>"},{"pid":"ea9a9d93a53d2ece9393e5388245020e1e866efa","tid":2332594,"uid":13100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T17:41:28.000Z","msg":"未出就比奬佢,間嘢收𠵇幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6bed7cb9cc609dfb4d0f3ab77d76274e9ded776","tid":2332594,"uid":46389,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T17:42:45.000Z","msg":"算唔算係歷史上最多獎嘅電子垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"928d432dbe51422c1291a74fe600396567aec2ab","tid":2332594,"uid":169195,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T18:49:55.000Z","msg":"出完先delay，係創新既"},{"pid":"dcaac59375357b9993d9fd1266336bf4e8b0381a","tid":2332594,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T04:53:07.000Z","msg":"宣傳費 主要係攞奬<img src=\"/as